@startuml
' @id(SEQ-RENDER-CYCLE-DIFF)
' @ref(USE-CYCLE-DIFF-VIEW)
' @ref(USE-DIFF-DIAGRAM)
'
' Objective-side flow for Diff mode. The view is keyed on the rail-
' selected file; the cycle is chosen only among cycles that actually
' changed that file (no global picker), defaulting to the latest. An
' inner toggle picks the Diagram sub-view (pre-rendered superposed
' .diff.svg on the canvas) or the List sub-view (per-file buckets).
'
' @desc(SEQ-RENDER-CYCLE-DIFF, "Diff mode lists only cycles that actually changed the rail-selected file — its CycleDiff has a non-empty added/removed set (a written .diff), not merely present-unchanged in the snapshot (default latest; caption if one; placeholder if none); Diagram paints that cycle's .diff.svg, List shows its buckets.")
title Render the selected file's cycle diff (objective)

actor "Developer" as Dev
participant "MddViewer\n(eframe::App)" as Viewer
participant "DiffView\n(selected cycle + file + sub-mode)" as DV
participant "CycleRegistry\n(mdd-core)" as Reg
database ".mdd/cycles/<n>/\nmanifest, before/, after/,\n<kind>/<name>.diff.puml" as Store
database ".mdd/rendered/cycles/<n>/\n<kind>/<name>.diff.svg" as Rendered
participant "DiagramPage\n(usvg/resvg)" as Page
participant "egui painter" as Painter

Dev -> Viewer : select model file F in the rail
Dev -> Viewer : open Diff mode
Viewer -> Reg : cycles_with_diff_for(F)
Reg -> Store : scan cycles + cycle_diffs per cycle
note right of Reg
  A cycle counts ONLY if it actually changed F —
  its CycleDiff for key(F) has a non-empty added
  or removed set (a written .diff.puml/.diff.svg).
  A file merely present unchanged in a cycle's
  before/after snapshot does NOT make the list.
end note
Reg --> DV : [cycles that changed key(F)]\n(newest first)
DV -> DV : key = kind(F) + "/" + name(F)

opt no cycle changed F
  DV -> Painter : text("This diagram didn't change in any cycle")
  Painter --> Dev : placeholder
end

alt exactly one such cycle
  DV -> Dev : caption "Cycle NNNN" (no control)
else several
  DV -> Dev : chips of ONLY those cycles\n(default = latest); pick one = N
end
DV -> DV : bind(cycle = N, file = F)

alt sub-mode = Diagram (default)
  DV -> Rendered : resolve .mdd/rendered/cycles/N/<kind>/<name>.diff.svg
  alt rendered SVG present
    Rendered --> Page : svg bytes
    Page -> Page : rasterize at base zoom (cached)
    loop each painted frame
      DV -> Painter : paint diff page (pan/zoom reused)
      note right of Painter
        SVG already carries <<added>> green
        and <<removed>> red skinparams baked
        in by SEQ-RENDER-DIFF-SVG.
      end note
      Painter --> Dev : superposed diff diagram
    end
  else rendered SVG missing
    DV -> Painter : text("No rendered diff — run the render pipeline")
    Painter --> Dev : placeholder
  end
else sub-mode = List
  DV -> DV : take CycleDiff(F).{unchanged, added, removed}
  DV -> Painter : shared neutral / added green / removed red (text)
  Painter --> Dev : per-file element buckets
end

opt cycle still Open (no after/)
  DV -> Painter : text("Diff available after the cycle closes")
  Painter --> Dev : placeholder
end
@enduml
